node.text:
So I was going to have my new desk set up today but the top was BROKEN. Now I have to wait for a replacement. RIP.⠀
⠀
Things have been moving pretty slowly, I apologize for the delay and appreciate your patience! We just got our mattress a few days ago, we've been sleeping on an air mattress for a month and apparently other furniture items are on backorder until JANUARY.⠀
⠀
I do still have my portable Mobile Studio Pro tablet though, but it's been acting up (it crashed while I was making this post) and I generally work slower on it. Still, I wanna get these cartoons made so I'll post more soon!

node.text:
It's been 6 months since Mega Man X stopped Sigma and his Maverick uprising.. But a familiar foe has returned for revenge! The new and improved.. Storm Eagle L! Watch the full video on Youtube, link in bio! #SomethingSeries #MegaManX #TerminalMontage⠀
Special thanks to @funymony for his amazing work on backgrounds! And @MyNewSoundtrack for his awesome Storm Eagle remix!!
